data.description:
Charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in Balch Springs, TX. This inviting residence boasts a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into the open-concept dining and kitchen area. The kitchen is a highlight, featuring a generously sized island, complemented by wood cabinetry and an attractive glass tile backsplash.The sizable master bedroom is illuminated by two windows that invite abundant natural light, while the master bathroom offers a single sink and a convenient bathtub-shower combination. The thoughtfully designed split bedroom floor plan situates the three additional bedrooms on the opposite side of the house, accompanied by a central bathroom for enhanced convenience .
Outside, the home boasts a substantial backyard, providing ample space for various outdoor activities. Additionally, a delightful seating area on the side of the house offers a cozy retreat. This property presents an ideal opportunity for comfortable family living within a well-designed space.
